{"parse":{"title":"Plated Armorfish","pageid":44841,"wikitext":{"*":"<onlyinclude>{{{{{tpl|tooltip}}}\n|mode={{{mode|}}}\n|arg={{{arg|}}}\n|quality=Common\n|name=Plated Armorfish\n|icon=INV_Misc_Fish_04\n|ilvl=55\n|sell={{cost|||70}}\n|stack=20\n}}</onlyinclude>\n\n== Source ==\n'''Plated Armorfish''' is a fish that can be fished in high level areas including [[Winterspring]], [[Eastern Plaguelands]], [[Dire Maul]], [[Zul'Gurub]], and [[Feralas]].  It has a higher drop rate during the night, while [[Lightning Eel]] has a higher drop rate during the day.\n\n== Plated Armorfish as an Ingredient ==\n\nPlated Armorfish is not used in cooking or alchemy.\n\n== Plated Armorfish as a quest objective ==\n*Before [[Patch 4.0.3]], was needed for {{questlong|Neutral|60|Craftsman's Writ - Plated Armorfish}} (30 required).\n\n== Patch changes ==\n* {{Patch 4.0.3|note=No longer a quest turn in.}}\n\n==External links==\n<!-- Read http://www.wowwiki.com/WoWWiki:External_links before posting your links here.\nLinks that do not conform to the rules will be DELETED.\nRepeat violations may result in a BAN.\nHave a nice day. :) -->\n{{elinks-item|13890}}\n{{Elink|link=http://www.elsanglin.com/fish/plated_armorfish.html |site=El's Extreme Anglin' |icon=elsanglin}}\n[[Category:World of Warcraft common fished items]]"}}}